item.title: About me
item.author: lucystreams+beautyblog@gmail.com (Lucy Rebekah)
item.description: My name is Lucy. Here are 5 facts about me: Normal to dry skin Neutral to cool toned skin ~NC10 Home country Australia, the western world’s desert wasteland of make up Favourite make up category is lipstick Can’t live without sunscreen Why makeup? I think most of us who love makeup have similar reasons. It’s a creative outlet. It’s relaxing and therapeutic, full of soothing scents and soft brushes.
